Name: The Court - Blanco/Grey
Body:
The Court is inspired by classic basketball heritage and is handmade in Italy by world renowned craftsmen using locally sourced premium Italian leather and luxurious suede accents for broken-in comfort.

The inside is lined with the same soft leather, making socks optional. The Court is lasted on top of an all-rubber Margom outsole to maximize comfort.

Body:
The Royale is a premium quality essential sneaker. Every pair is handmade in Italy by world renowned craftsmen using only luxury materials like full grain leather (the type that truly gets better with age). The inside is lined with the same supple leather, making socks optional.

Every pair arrives with a set of waxed-cotton laces that will develop a unique patina of their own.

Name: The Royale Knit - Navy/White
Body:
Meet the Royale Knit - designed in Brooklyn, made in Italy from recycled ocean and single-use plastics. Each pair is the equivalent of recycling 7 plastic bottles! Based on our best selling style, the Royale Knit is lightweight & breathable, about the average weight of a running shoe. Every pair is fitted with custom performance insoles to maximize comfort.

By wearing the Royale Knit, you are contributing to GREATS' mission to have clean oceans around the world. Available for men and women in multiple colors who believe in being, "Better Than".

Name: The Court - Light Pink
Body:
The Court is inspired by classic basketball heritage and is handmade in Italy by world renowned craftsmen using locally sourced premium Italian leather and luxurious suede accents for broken-in comfort.

The inside is lined with the same soft leather, making socks optional. The Court is lasted on top of an all-rubber Margom outsole to maximize comfort.

The Court is inspired by classic basketball heritage and is handmade in Italy by world renowned craftsmen using locally sourced premium Italian leather and luxurious suede accents for broken-in comfort.

The inside is lined with the same soft leather, making socks optional. The Court is lasted on top of an all-rubber Margom outsole to maximize comfort.

This seasonal style features durable ballistic nylon for year-round wear. The inside is lined with supple perforated leather, making socks optional.
